<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٣٥:</span> مَا الْأَمْوَالُ الَّتِي تَجِبُ فِيهَا الزَّكَاةُ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الْأَمْوَالُ الَّتِي تَجِبُ فِيهَا الزَّكَاةُ خَمْسَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> السَّائِمَةُ مِنْ بَهِيمَةِ الْأَنْعَامِ:</span> وَهِيَ الْإِبِلُ وَالْبَقَرُ وَالْغَنَمُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - الْخَارِجُ مِنَ الْأَرْضِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> النَّقْدَانِ:</span> وَهُمَا الذَّهَبُ وَالْفِضَّةُ، وَكَذَلِكَ مَا يَقُومُ مَقَامَهُمَا مِنَ الْعُمْلَاتِ الْوَرَقيَّةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤ - عَرُوضُ التِّجَارَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥ - الْمَعَادِنُ وَالرِّكَازُ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٣٦:</span> مَا شُرُوطُ وُجُوبِ الزَّكَاةِ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>شُرُوطُ وُجُوبِ الزَّكَاةِ أَرْبَعَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - الْإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - الْحُرِّيَّةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣ - مِلْكُ النِّصَابِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) المَعَادنُ: هِي كُلُّ مَا خرَجَ مِنَ الأرْضِ ممَّا يُخلَقُ فِيهَا مِنْ غَيرِها ممَّا لَهُ قِيمَةٌ.<br>والرِّكازُ: هُو مَا يُوجدُ فِي الأرْضِ مِنْ دَفْنِ الجَاهليَّةِ.</p> </div>